window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>New York Times </i></b><b>Bestselling Author Laura Scott</b></p> <p><i>Search and rescue and love…</i></p> <p><i>Accident or Murder?</i></p> <p>When Kendra Sullivan reaches out to Dominic Lakeland, the son of the pilot who was killed alongside her parents six years ago, she is hopeful they will finally uncover the truth about that fateful day. But when bullets start to fly targeting Dominic, it’s clear the past has collided with the present.</p> <p>Dominic hates knowing he’d inadvertently dragged Kendra into danger, but as they learn more about the man who’d killed his father, he understands the threat is bigger than he could have imagined. He needs Kendra and her siblings to help him uncover the truth. Dominic knows he’ll protect Kendra with his life, but will he risk his heart to find love at Christmas?</p>"; 
